{"tid":1989430,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭若驊：政府一向尊重和保障人權和自由，但並非絕對","createTime":"2020-04-26T03:27:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T13:53:19.000Z","uid":212626,"like":10,"dislike":317,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"f7ce645cc691b5dfd6c5d42c65ea153d48879857","tid":1989430,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:27:50.000Z","msg":"律政司司長鄭若驊在網誌表示，律政司檢控人員履行職務時不應該受任何涉及政治因素的影響，案件亦不會因任何人的政治理念而在處理上有所不同。鄭若驊強調，根據基本法規定，律政司的刑事檢控工作不受任何干涉，包括來自外國政客的要求；若果有人發表言論，企圖令政府改變檢控決定甚至放棄檢控，都是嚴重違反法治精神。<span style=\"color: red;\">她稱有人提出律政司的檢控是「政治檢控」只是錯誤理解，而不論是富豪或是政治人物，都不能凌駕法律</span>，稱律政司處理時會一視同仁。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊又稱，當案件由執法機構完成刑事調查，向律政司徵詢法律意見時，律政司檢控人員會仔細考慮，除非檢控人員相信有充份證據支持提出檢控，有合理機會達致定罪，否則是不會提出檢控。而一旦展開司法程序，任何人都不應加以評論；若果有人要求律政司放棄檢控、或企圖左右律政司決定都會徒勞無功。她強調，<span style=\"color: red;\">政府一向尊重和保障人權和自由，但相關權利並非絕對，法律對權利的行使有明確限制</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1283445&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1283445%26csid%3D261_341&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=0595d6df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1283445&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"703f69870ed430e8757bfb9ded88b040b35538bf","tid":1989430,"uid":41873,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:28:32.000Z","msg":"屌你老母做雞俾狗屌"},{"pid":"1f74f0ac7d3fc6633056c2c899cc83fab29ce8eb","tid":1989430,"uid":205162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ab7eb7e315dc8664da66f23af10ccd8e8d63a7","tid":1989430,"uid":67454,"like":64,"dislike":2,"score":62,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:29:49.000Z","msg":"讀過social contract未?"},{"pid":"a26d9c99a3f92ce4cf3d9b6708bdbe3f7cff6460","tid":1989430,"uid":225130,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:30:08.000Z","msg":"慳d啦<br />\n有前設既自由做係撚自由<br />\n<br />\n黑警 黑社會，仲有你本人，有撚受法律制裁咩"},{"pid":"ed1f7aedeb2b1781e5b6c30812b741a76733cb1a","tid":1989430,"uid":301666,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:30:18.000Z","msg":"邊條法例容許警察濫暴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3d326effb8645b97293bbc306148afb164b1aa","tid":1989430,"uid":189046,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:30:30.000Z","msg":"鄭若驊：政府有權踐踏人權和自由<br />\n等制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732c06e372b36be5eb7e9622d4e5ae537a9d219a","tid":1989430,"uid":225130,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:31:36.000Z","msg":"除非檢控人員相信有充份證據支持提出檢控，有合理機會達致定罪，否則是不會提出檢控。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n丫叉個單?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n區軒入到罪又係乜原因?<br />\n暴動現場經過就拉哂告哂，又係乜?<br />\n<br />\n梗係有機會定罪啦，法官咁高尚情操"},{"pid":"5e8a33eb15e495e30a89edcd83e3244d6ccd71c1","tid":1989430,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:32:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852d2ee9aeffe05edd059258756205cc9123fbdb","tid":1989430,"uid":53003,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:33:17.000Z","msg":"而不論是富豪或是政治人物，都不能凌駕法律<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EAF3b-bUIAAPnJX?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEAF3b-bUIAAPnJX%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=e566f768&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fbi0r0E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F